</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li> <p>TAB completion</p> </li>
<li> <p>Keyboard shortcuts</p> </li>
<li> <p>Quotes handling in Spring Shell</p> </li>
<li> <p>Quotes handling in Data Flow DSL</p> </li>
</ul>
</div>
<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/uyN8ttlTvUM" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
